metadata.name: DAO.exe
metadata.description:
A long time ago in a galaxy far, far away....  

A deep void persisted for countless light years.  
There were no pixels on the screen, no MIDI and no bytes.  
But then, something extraordinary happened.

The simplest programs started to take shape and spontaneously evolved into sentient algorithms.  Over time, these algorithms defined properties to generate the first geometry and grid. 

Thus a magical universe was born.  They call it Feisty DAO - the custodian of culture, games, art, music, and memes.  Feat. Path, Cobie, Rookie, TDHD, Eiko, Dresdlr, Ultron, Yahzman & Reuben.
